{"tid":1581920,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中共為左抹黑我地香港 展開左暗黑文宣 去抹黑醜化我地","createTime":"2019-09-19T21:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T17:51:12.000Z","uid":222970,"like":43,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8cb8427e165c01c5c058d05d602d602bc2c9d46a","tid":1581920,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T21:08:46.000Z","msg":"#在抖音，记录美好生活#9月17日，#乌蛟腾烈士碑被涂污。香港市民痛哭失声，泪流满面。 <a href=\"http://v.douyin.com/mPTkmY/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.douyin.com%2FmPTkmY%2F%20&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IPz4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=0dc83e0f\" target=\"_blank\">http://v.douyin.com/mPTkmY/ </a>复制此链接，打开【抖音短视频】，直接观看视频！<br />\n<br />\n中共只係派自己人 假扮示威者 去塗鴉抗日墓碑<br />\n<br />\n仲拍埋玩煽情 為左激化大陸人對我地香港既仇恨<br />\n<br />\n依件事上左weibo熱門第九位 有5000萬人睇左<br />\n<br />\n一單既塗鴉事件已經覆蓋左我地反攻大陸既文宣<br />\n<br />\n佢依種既嫁禍手段 低成本 低風險 高回報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地真係應該向中共學習 分化手段 嫁禍手段"},{"pid":"e2bc0eae36bd00924895b2350d124d315e3050bd","tid":1581920,"uid":294,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T21:10:22.000Z","msg":"你有無諗過中共果班智障根本唔會反共"},{"pid":"f76043ef8cb7869f81e7ad8e807bdaf4b1413a0e","tid":1581920,"uid":222970,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T21:13:03.000Z","msg":"中共學人講愛國？學人講反日？<br />\n<br />\n中共為左鞏固地位，出賣國家尊嚴人民都在所不惜<br />\n<br />\n班大陸人仲on99咁 以為中共係為國家而反日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1XLRXkc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XLRXkc.jpg&h=0fc4150f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/giaRXkk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgiaRXkk.jpg&h=5f99602d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e65b274af1892d232681f831d9424c1c50dc5150","tid":1581920,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T21:13:32.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{